{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we sang Jewish songs and we got lectures about Judaism and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's quite innocent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was quite an innocent situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not boy meet girl, though there were boys and girls together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and so from there, these were my-- essentially my activities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I also read a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I began to read the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I bought different newspapers, different newspapers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I realized different-- sort of different opinions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But at 14 years old, already did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I used to read a newspaper from page one to the last page, like, you know nothing, no selectivity, but just get ideas of that newspaper.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that kept me while I was going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So all these, between them, there really wasn't much time left except to eat and sleep after all these activities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so-- and then-- then, at age 16, I didn't-- I sort of didn't like the factory anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I wanted-- somebody told me about another area called diamond mounting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think I had a stye in my eye.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Some dust came into my head, and like, you know, had problems with my eye.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because of that, because of dust getting in my-- so I wanted to leave that factory, and I did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and I got a job in-- in what they call Manhattan Garden, the diamond area, district area in London.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in-- must have been in 1945, in-- middle of '45 somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got a job there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've worked in that for a year, 'til '47.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I wanted to go to hakhshara.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because of my involvement with B'nai Akiva and the ideology towards hakhshara.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to go-- hakhshara means preparation.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
